s. Additionally, there are techniques like deep learning, which involve using neural networks with multiple layers to learn hierarchical representations from data, often achieving state-of-the-art performance in various tasks.</font></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.25em; border: 0px solid rgb(217, 217, 227); --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(69,89,164,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-backdrop-hue-rotate: ; --tw-backdrop-invert: ; --tw-backdrop-opacity: ; --tw-backdrop-saturate: ; --tw-backdrop-sepia: ; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><font color=\"#636363\" face=\"Helvetica\">Machine learning has found applications in numerous fields, such as finance, healthcare, marketing, recommendation systems, autonomous vehicles, and more. The availability of large datasets and advances in computing power have significantly contributed to the growth and success of machine learning in recent years</font></p><div><font color=\"#636363\" face=\"Helvetica\"><br></font></div></h5>', '2023-07-30 01:58:57', '2023-07-30 03:07:42', 1, 'Machine-Learning', 'e1a116d1307ebdc9e925ee53b1df9